{"tid":1621283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：所謂引蛇出洞。你不是蛇，就不必出動。泛民就配合政府去舉動示威集會。這些都是trap-setting（佈置陷阱）","createTime":"2019-10-04T13:04:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T16:00:04.000Z","uid":241151,"like":18,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"fddb3b4d7568842f6752db04635d59d824fb4332","tid":1621283,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T13:04:07.000Z","msg":"陳雲：所謂引蛇出洞。你不是蛇，就不必出動。政府發揮它在山竹超級颱風都不可用的影響力，今日全港學校和辦公室提早放，店鋪關門，公司提早叫人走，大家得閒在街上在商場，泛民就配合政府去舉動示威集會。這些都是trap-setting（佈置陷阱），而且是毛澤東的「陽謀」的級數。<br />\n各國的經驗證明，反蒙面法沒有效果。香港特首動用英王的王權賦予的《緊急法》來訂立禁止蒙面法，必會遇到司法覆核，過不了幾日，毋須去打它而令它可以發生效用。"},{"pid":"986bf44870386aa0678ccb2dc11967b39f845cca","tid":1621283,"uid":140326,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T13:08:06.000Z","msg":"我呢個泛民左膠表示 今次認同陳雲講野<br />\n今次幫你推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5dcb216b6425b533dd5e0b44a37e7547d7de6f9","tid":1621283,"uid":159913,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T13:08:42.000Z","msg":"陳雲又嚟怨婦mode<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bdfbdcd7c3ad9764316c413783159a99a432f73","tid":1621283,"uid":50386,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T13:09:39.000Z","msg":"又關泛民咩事"},{"pid":"1962d6262bc632d1214775b516201a6f3e0403bd","tid":1621283,"uid":263261,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T13:10:31.000Z","msg":"關泛民咩事<br />\n乜都關泛民事<br />\n怨婦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6797826530f3d6f69bccf3ae3d67b61ae1fcd3f","tid":1621283,"uid":288523,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T13:15:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2026e1a7bf32c3634e7647bda51bb546a80a8f6e","tid":1621283,"uid":191790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"986bf44870386aa0678ccb2dc11967b39f845cca","tid":1621283,"uid":140326,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019